snippet.title: Gunslugs:Rogue Tactics GAMEPLAY (alpha build 0.0.13)
snippet.description:
A much overdue gameplay update for Gunslugs:Rogue Tactics. More info on the game: https://www.orangepixel.net/gunslugs3/

__

I'm Pascal a Dutch independent game developer since 2004 known as Orangepixel. I talk about my games, my days and my experiences. Follow me?  I post a new video once a week.

I've made various playlists for easy access to different topics: https://www.youtube.com/user/orangepixelmobile/playlists
__

If you want exclusive sketches and behind the scenes info delivered to your mail box, sign-up here:
http://www.orangepixel.net/sign-up/

You can also come hang out in the Discord: https://discord.gg/jYr6XVC

Or be a PATRON: http://patreon.com/orangepixel

__
